sentences.english: The jovian moon Io harbors a globe-girdling pool of molten rock beneath its volcano- riddled surface.
sentences.chinese: 木衛一佈滿火山的表面下擁有一個包圍全球的熔岩池。

sentences.english: Io is largely molten silicate rock with an iron core.
sentences.chinese: 木衛一主要是熔化的鐵與硅酸鹽岩石的核心。
